Package checkers.flow

Contains a generalized flow-sensitive qualifier inference that can be employed by any checker.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Flow
    Interface for a generalized flow-sensitive qualifier inference for the checkers framework.
    FlowState
    The state that is managed by a flow inference implementation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractFlow<ST extends FlowState>
    Provides a generalized flow-sensitive qualifier inference for the checkers framework.
    DefaultFlow<ST extends DefaultFlowState>
    The default implementation of the flow-sensitive type inference.
    DefaultFlowState
    Stores the annotation that is inferred for each variable.
    GenKillBits<K extends @Nullable Object>
    Maintains multiple gen-kill sets, "keyed" by a value.
